text.tspan: Defeat 3 more times to complete the

g.aria-label:
Impossibly small timekeeping device, traded from a strange creature who held no knowledge of its value.
Glass covering needs replacing.

text.tspan: May your tendons peel like bark, your flesh scoured with it.
May your tongue be cast out from your mind by our own.
May your meat become silk, your mind become soul,
the matter displaced like dregs to the ground.
May you wake up, no longer beast you knew.
May every piece of your selfhood sliver one by one.
May you never know if you are the same you as yesterday.
